						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone in front of the temple of Honnēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragment of a damaged record seems to record a gift of land to a deity. <hi rend="bold">Maḻāvaḷḷi</hi> (village ?) and <hi rend="bold">Māda-gāmuṇḍa</hi> are mentioned. The characters are of about the <hi rend="bold">8th century A.D.</hi> </p>						

